States:

EmptyState
GameBeginningState
CharactersListingState
CharacterCreatingState
GameBuildingState
ExplorationState
BattleState
GameSavingState
GameLoadingState
GameEndingState

Actions:

BeginGameAction
ChooseCharacterAction
CreateCharacterAction
BuildGameAction
ExploreAction
FightAction
SaveGameAction
LoadGameAction
EndGameAction

Transitions:

From						To 							Action 						Conditions
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
EmptyState                  GameBeginningState          BeginGameAction             No Condition
GameBeginningState			CharactersListingState		ChooseCharacterAction		Player Chose To Play A New Game
GameBeginningState			GameLoadingState			LoadGameAction				Player Chose To Load A Saved Game
CharactersListingState		CharacterCreatingState		CreateCharacterAction		Create Character Selected
CharactersListingState		GameBuildingState			BuildGameAction        		Listed Character Selected
CharactersListingState		GameEndingState				EndGame        		Exit Requested
CharacterCreatingState		CharactersListingState		ChooseCharacterEvent		Character Created
CharacterCreatingState		GameEndingState				EndGameEvent        		Exit Requested
GameBuildingState           ExplorationState            ExploreEvent                Game Built
ExplorationState			BattleState					FightEvent  				Enemy Found In The Room Explored
ExplorationState			GameEndingState				EndGameEvent				Exit Requested
BattleState					ExplorationState			ExploreEvent				Enemy Defeated
BattleState					GameEndingState				EndGameEvent				Player Defeated or Exit Requested
GameLoadingState			ExplorationState			ExploreEvent				Loaded Game Was Saved While Exploring
GameLoadingState			BattleState					FightEvent  				Loaded Game Was Saved While Fighting
ExplorationState			GameSavingState				SaveGameEvent				Player Chose To Save Game While Exploring
BattleState					GameSavingState				SaveGameEvent				Player Chose To Save Game While Fighting
GameSavingState				ExplorationState			ExploreEvent				Game Saved And Returned To Exploration State
GameSavingState				BattleState					FightEvent  				Game Saved And Returned To Battle State

